description: Lists, in descending order, the sessions that have been created in a notebook that are in an active state like CREATING, CREATED, IDLE or BUSY. Newer sessions are listed first; older sessions are listed later.

parameters.name: NotebookId
parameters.description: The ID of the notebook to list sessions for.

nested_items.name: NotebookSessionsList
nested_items.description: A list of the sessions belonging to the notebook.

nested_items.name: CreationTime
nested_items.description: The time when the notebook session was created.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: A token generated by the Athena service that specifies where to continue pagination if a previous request was truncated. To obtain the next set of pages, pass in the NextToken from the response object of the previous page call.
